		<title>Keyboard Shortcuts</title>
		<para>
			To define keyboard as, for example,
			<shortcut>
				<keycombo>
					<keycap>Ctrl</keycap>
					<keycap>Space</keycap>
				</keycombo>
			</shortcut>,
			use the following
		</para>
		<programlisting language="xml">
			<xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
				parse="text" href="./examples/gui/shortcut.xml" />
		</programlisting>
	</section>
</section>
